{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_07_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 私のプライドはズタズタよ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……いい話なのは、確かなんだけど\nこの仕事、やっぱり私には合わないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……It’s a good offer‚ no doubt about it.\nBut this job just isn't for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロには私よりふさわしい子達がいるでしょう？\n彼女達に頼んだ方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are girls at Hoshimi Prods more suited for it than me‚ right?\nIt'd be better to ask them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先方が莉央さんにぜひ頼みたいそうなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The client specifically wants you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今までにない花嫁像を表現して顧客拡大に繋げたい\n莉央さんとなら、それが出来ると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want to expand their customer base by showcasing a new type of bride.\nThey believe that can be achieved with you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でもブライダルのテレビCMでしょ？\nウエディングドレスを着て、にっこり笑う感じよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's for a bridal TV commercial‚ right?\nI'd have to wear a wedding dress and smile sweetly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのを否定する訳じゃないけど……\n私のイメージだと、似合わないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not against that kind of thing‚ but…\nIsn't that image a poor fit for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、クールでかっこいい花嫁を表現したいから\n莉央さんの凛とした雰囲気がぴったりなんだそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ they want to portray a cool and stylish bride.\nThey think your dignified aura is perfect for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方のプロデューサーは\n莉央さん以外に考えられない、と言っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The client’s producer said\nthey couldn’t think of anyone else but you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方、随分熱心にこの仕事を勧めるわね\nいつもなら、本人の意向が一番です、って言うじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re really pushing this job hard‚ aren’t you?\nUsually‚ you’re all about respecting my wishes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4955797791,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}